---
title: Chicken, Leek & Bacon Pie with Mash Topping & Parsley
description: We think the world's a better place when there's chicken pie for dinner! With a garlic and herb-seasoned bacon and leek filling
and heavenly mashed potato topping (which the kids can help out with), this is just what we all need right now.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/651a22d9f20f270b56d71a36-c0a7cd7f.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/651a22d9f20f270b56d71a36.pdf
